This repository contains the files required to recreate the board support designs for the alveo platforms, to enable use with the casper design flow.

Please ensure that you have at Vivado 2021.1 installed and the correct board support package for your hardware.
Alveo U50: xilinx.com:au50:part0:1.2
Alveo U280: xilinx.com:au50:part???

To create the Vivado project

change your directory into the folder of the tcl script you would like to run. eg au50_bsp
source the settings64.sh script in your Vivado install directory ()
Start vivado
in the tcl command line run "source au50_bsp.tcl"

Ensure that you have the board files for your target platform installed otherwise the script will fail


